summary: This isn't a question, but I saw that in the latest series of captain marvel, in the upcoming issue 4, Carol's about to go fight...
question: This isn't a question, but I saw that in the latest series of captain marvel, in the upcoming issue 4, Carol's about to go fight Rogue again, and I'm crossing fingers about them being finally friends, heck the cover is a parallel to a classic fight between them.
answer: Freaking Marvel. I know Rouge screwed up, but you know, she was sort of screwed up in general then. She’s come a long damn way, and I do not want to see these two fighting again. Just … come on marvel.

summary: One of my fears for endgame is that tony stark survives, but not all of him does. What if he returns half the man he was? What...
body:
One of my fears for endgame is that tony stark survives, but not all of him does. What if he returns half the man he was? What if he comes back but it’s not the true him? He’s already lost so much, and he just keeps losing things. If his mind can no longer function as it could before? And what if it wasn’t because he was trying to save someone? Would he regret what he did?


But then again I’m sure marvels gonna do something hella worse

blog.description: this blog is about my crushes, something like my diary,

summary: Mattie 🤦💜🖤
body:
Mattie 🤦💜🖤

Update, we’re still together, people know about us, we’re happy, well at least it looks like it from his part, I am happy for sure.

So as I said, update.

Almost every weekend I’m at his place. When my school day ends, I go to his flat, turn on heating and wait for him about hour and half. Then when he comes home we eat something, nothing cooked since he doesn’t have kitchen yet, and watch movies.

Marvel movies. Yep that’s right, I, a big MARVEL nerd have persuaded my boyfriend, who said he will never, ever, watch marvel ‘cause he hates superheroes, to watch Deadpool and he loved it obviously. Then he asked me to watch another marvel movie, so after short chat with my soulmate Barbi (who is my bestest friend, my soulmate, my love, my classmate and we share the same desk at school, always) who told me to start at the beginning, obviously with Iron Man, we started the whole Avengers timeline, and now every day he is like “yesssss, we’re gonna watch marvel” I am so proud of myself, him.

It brings me joy to see his reactions and that childlike excitement on his face.

Conclusion, he hates Captain’s America guts, his literall words “Why is he there, he’s not cool, he’s not Thor nor Iron Man, I want Deadpool to be there instead of him” 😂😂😂😂😂

I almost busted out laughing, I mean I don’t like Captain either, but this was so….. sincere

Now it’s Saturday morning here, 10:11 am, he’s at work, I’m gonna eat something and then study, and when he comes home from work we will continue our marathon.

So that’s the update.
